**Auth:** JWT + Approved

**Description:** Create an intro request. Enforces tier intro limits (`403 INTRO_LIMIT_REACHED` when exceeded).

**Body:**

| Field | Type | Required |
|-------|------|----------|
| `toUserId` | UUID | yes |
