| `message` | string (max 1000) | no |

**Example request:**

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:4000/api/intros \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "toUserId": "b2222222-2222-4222-8222-222222222222",
    "reason": "investment",
    "message": "Raising Series A — would value your perspective."
  }'
